<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body { 
          background: #f4f1e8; 
          color: #2c1810; 
          margin: 0; 
          padding: 20px;
          line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .newspaper {
          max-width: 800px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          background: #faf8f3;
          padding: 40px;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      .masthead {
          text-align: center;
          border-bottom: 3px solid #8b0000;
          padding-bottom: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .title {
          font-size: 3.5rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          letter-spacing: 2px;
          margin: 0;
          text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      .subtitle {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          font-style: italic;
          margin: 10px 0 0 0;
          color: #666;
      }
      .headline {
          font-size: 2rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 30px 0 20px 0;
          border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
          padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .columns {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
          gap: 30px;
          margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .article {
          text-align: justify;
          font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .court-form {
          background: #fff;
          border: 2px solid #8b0000;
          padding: 25px;
          margin: 30px 0;
          text-align: center;
      }
      .submit-btn {
          background: #8b0000;
          color: white;
          border: none;
          padding: 12px 30px;
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          cursor: pointer;
          margin-top: 15px;
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      }
      .submit-btn:hover {
          background: #660000;
      }
      .word-input {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          padding: 10px;
          border: 2px solid #333;
          margin: 0 10px;
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="newspaper">
      <div class="masthead">
        <h1 class="title">WORD COURT</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">The People's Tribune for Disputed Word Legality</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 5px 0 0 0;">
          Est. 2024 • Serving Word Game Enthusiasts Everywhere
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="headline">
        AI JUSTICES READY TO HEAR YOUR CASE
      </div>

      <div class="columns">
        <div class="article">
          <p>
            <strong>BREAKING:</strong>
            Revolutionary three-judge AI panel now available to settle word disputes that have plagued casual Scrabble players for decades.
          </p>
          <p>
            The innovative court system features a prosecuting AI that argues against questionable words, a defending AI that advocates for word validity, and a presiding judge AI that weighs all evidence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="article">
          <p>
            Cases are heard in real-time with full transparency. All arguments, evidence, and reasoning are preserved for the court record.
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>"No more family arguments over whether 'qi' is a real word,"</em>
            says Chief Digital Justice. <em>"We'll settle it once and for all."</em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="court-form">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #8b0000;">SUBMIT YOUR CASE</h2>
        <p>Present your disputed word to our esteemed AI judicial panel</p>
        <div>
          <input type="text" class="word-input" placeholder="Enter disputed word" maxlength="20" />
          <button class="submit-btn">PRESENT TO COURT</button>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 15px; color: #666;">
          Court is in session 24/7 • No appointment necessary
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888;">
        Word Court Gazette • Volume 1, Issue 1 • Digital Edition
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
